how do you think i feel leading the three tenors mehta 
asked its a dream 
with the tenors providing enough sonic booms organizers said 
air traffic officials at romes leonardo da vinci airport agreed to 
reroute flight paths so planes wont be flying over the 
1800yearold ruins of the public baths 
there are only 6000 seats amid the ruins where several operas 
are performed during the summer and about 100000 wouldbe 
concertgoers were left disappointed organizers said 
there was more pressure to get a ticket to the concert than to 
the final of the world cup on sunday evening rome mayor franco 
carraro said 
sales of tickets ranging from 25 to 335 yielded 1 
million organizers said 
the three tenors agreed to sing without pay and will donate to 
charity their share of revenues from television showings ticket 
sales as well as sales of videos cassettes and albums from the 
concert which will be recorded 
our pay is being together in this marvelous musical and 
human circumstance pavarotti said 
domingo born in spain but raised in mexico said four mexican 
villages devastated by an earthquake in 1985 will benefit from his 
share carreras who battled back from leukemia said hell donate 
his proceeds to foundations fighting the disease pavarottis share 
will help benefit sufferers of a variety of diseases as well as a 
marrow transplant center in pesaro italy 
pavarotti said the three agreed to do it in part because 
carreras back to the stage after his illness is so exceptional 
and because the soccer championship is such an important moment it 
wouldnt have been possible in any other moment 
