this is how the first class to enter beijing university after 
last years democracy movement spent the school year learning to 
be good foot soldiers of the communist revolution 
their training reflects the chinese leaderships analysis of the 
root cause of the massive 1989 studentled protests weak 
ideological education its prescription for preventing further 
unrest is to intensify political training and discipline 
while older beijing university students passed the school year 
in glum cynicism after the violent quashing of the movement they 
helped lead the 728 freshmen spent 10 months training at 
shijiazhuang 
