influenced the decision jeffrey said 
the headliner room opened with eddie fisher as its top act in 
1966 and featured such stars as sammy davis jr danny thomas 
patti page and bill cosby during its heyday 
after its conversion the room will stay roughly the same size 
seating 400 to 450 people 
the loss of the headliner room will leave the reno area with 
only three stages designed for topname acts ballys the sparks 
nugget and the flamingo hilton 
