billion from british airways plc but will have to wait for word on 
whether it receives an order from ual corp that could be worth 20 
billion unions trying to buy ual delayed negotiations on their 
potentially record jetliner order until they secure financing for 
their acquisition of the airline company 
brokers who belly up to the bar could be in for a doubly 
unpleasant tax surprise the federal government seeking ways to 
raise tax revenues to close the federal budget deficit is 
considering a 05 percent levy on securities sales and may seek to 
sharply raise the excise tax on alcohol 
